            "title": "恒指季檢寧德洛鉬老鋪黃金染藍 中升出局",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指公司公布，加入寧德時代(03750)、洛陽欒川鉬業(03993)及老鋪黃金(06181)入恒指成份股，剔除中升控股(00881)，成份股數目由88隻至90隻。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"寧德時代 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250602_FI_source-ap_03750-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"寧德時代 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250602_FI_source-ap_03750-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">寧德時代 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
